5. Activity Flow Chính
Đăng ký: mở RegisterScreen -> nhập thông tin -> optional chọn avatar -> AuthNotifier.register() -> AuthRepository.registerWithEmail() -> tạo Firebase user -> tạo Firestore profile -> upload avatar nếu có -> update profile -> schedule reminder -> Home.
Đăng nhập: LoginScreen -> nhập email/password hoặc Google -> AuthNotifier -> AuthRepository -> Firebase/Google -> load profile -> schedule reminder -> Home.
Đăng xuất: AccountScreen -> xác nhận -> AuthNotifier.logout() -> FirebaseAuth/GoogleSignIn signOut -> clear state -> AuthGate.
Flashcard: chọn topic -> load words/progress/favorites -> xem mặt trước -> flip mặt sau/TTS/favorite -> mark known hoặc unknown -> save progress -> hoàn thành -> reset/review unknown.
Quiz: chọn topic -> load words/progress -> build session seed/options -> user chọn answer/skip hoặc timer hết -> save -> next -> finish -> review wrong/reset.
Writing: chọn topic -> load session -> chọn ký tự -> vẽ strokes -> có thể xem đáp án/stroke order/TTS -> mark correct/wrong/skip -> save -> finish/review wrong.
Speaking: chọn topic -> load session -> TTS nghe mẫu -> start record -> stop -> speech_to_text -> tính điểm -> save -> replay/record again/next/review low score.
Game: chọn topic -> load words -> tạo hanzi/meaning items -> chọn hai bên -> đúng thì matched, sai thì highlight -> hint/reset -> finish -> save stats.
Search: load all words/history/favorites -> update query/filter -> normalize query -> filter -> submit lưu history -> favorite/TTS từ kết quả.
Upload avatar: Account/Register -> image_picker -> Cloudinary multipart upload -> nhận secure_url -> update Firestore + Firebase user photoURL.
