Flashcard: User -> FlashcardScreen -> FlashcardNotifier -> WordRepository(JSON) + FlashcardProgressRepository(Firestore/Prefs) + FavoritesRepository + TtsRepository
Quiz: User -> QuizScreen -> QuizNotifier -> WordRepository -> QuizProgressRepository -> LearningActivityRepository
Writing: User -> WritingScreen -> WritingNotifier -> WordRepository -> StrokeOrderRepository/TtsRepository/HandwritingRecognitionRepository -> WritingProgressRepository -> LearningActivityRepository
Speaking: User -> SpeakingScreen -> SpeakingNotifier -> AudioRecordingRepository -> SpeechRecognitionRepository -> SpeakingProgressRepository -> LearningActivityRepository
Game: User -> MatchingGameScreen -> MatchingGameNotifier -> WordRepository -> MatchingGameProgressRepository -> Firestore/Prefs
Search: User -> SearchScreen -> SearchNotifier -> WordRepository + SearchHistoryRepository + FavoritesRepository + TtsRepository
Avatar: User -> AccountScreen/AuthNotifier -> AvatarRepository -> Cloudinary HTTP -> AuthRepository -> Firestore/FirebaseAuth profile
